biotools.summary: ANISE (grAphical coNfigurator of TiFoSi In Silico Experiments) is an application that allows you to configure the input file of TiFoSi (Tissues: Forces & Signalling) which is a computational tool to simulate the cellular dynamics of planar epithelia.
